***** Course Meeting Times *****
Lectures: 2 sessions / week, 1.5 hours / session
Recitations: 1 session / week, 1.5 hours / session
***** Course Requirements *****
Problem sets are an integral part of the course. You are encouraged to work on
the problem sets in groups but you must turn in your own individual work. You
have one week to turn in each problem set. TA sessions will be devoted to the
solution of the previous week's problem set and some extra material not covered
in the lectures.
***** Grading *****
The final grade will be a weighted average of the problems sets and the final
exam. The final exam will be during the time of our last scheduled class.
   Grading criteria.
ACTIVITIES   PERCENTAGES
Problem Sets 30%
Final Exam   70%

